# API Request Pattern

**One line:** Loader extracts URL params, validates, calls API service; response hooks validate with type guards and update store via standalone setters (see zustand-memo-optimization.mdc).

## Overview
This rule defines the standard pattern for implementing API requests in the codebase, focusing on the React Router loader pattern for data fetching with clear separation of concerns.

